Package: katherinemansfieldr
Title: A Package for Text Mining Katherine Mansfield's Short Stories
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Andrew", "Kim", email = "akim17@amherst.edu",
                  role = c("aut", "cre")),
           person("Olivia", "Xu", email = "sxu17@amherst.edu",
                  role = c("aut")))
Description: This package contains machine45readable versions of the short stories from three of 
Katherine Mansfield's collections: The Garden Party, Bliss and Something Childish.
This package also contains functions that parse text files and perform stylometric analysis tasks such as
measuring lengths of sentences and words, measuring vocabulary richness, frequency of words and punctuation.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
